{"word":"δεικτέος","slug":"δεικτέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δεικτέος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δείκνυμι'><el>δείκνυμι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be shown</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>δεικτέον μοι</el> <i>it is</i> my <i>duty to show</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}